<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="T" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Thinking" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Thinking,</orth> subst. (cf. <emph>Think</emph>), thought: <cit><quote>I am wrapped in dismal --s,</quote> <bibl n="shak. aww 5.3.128" default="NO" valid="yes">All's V, 3, 128</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>his --s are below the moon,</quote> <bibl n="shak. h8 3.2.134" default="NO" valid="yes">H8 III, 2, 134</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>speak to me as to thy --s,</quote> <bibl n="shak. oth 3.3.131" default="NO" valid="yes">Oth. III, 3, 131</bibl></cit>. cf. <bibl n="shak. wiv 3.2.31" default="NO" valid="yes">Wiv. III, 2, 31</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. ayl 5.2.55" default="NO" valid="yes">As V, 2, 55</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. cor 4.6.31" default="NO" valid="yes">Cor. IV, 6, 31</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tim 1.1.219" default="NO" valid="yes">Tim. I, 1, 219</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. oth 1.2.76" default="NO" valid="yes">Oth. I, 2, 76</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. oth 2.3.344" default="NO" valid="yes">II, 3, 344</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. cym 1.4.157" default="NO" valid="yes">Cymb. I, 4, 157</bibl>.
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>